<designrules>
<description language="de">&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
&lt;b&gt;EAGLE design rules (DRU) for the Eurocircuits STANDARD pool service &lt;/b&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
The design rule parameters in this DRU file have been set to the minimum values compatible with our STANDARD pool service. The options Shapes and Misc are not relevant. Values for Roundness (Shapes) are not critical and can be set as you require. You can set the values for covered or “tented” via holes under Masks (Limit).
You can set larger minimum values if you wish but if you change to smaller minimum values your design cannot be made on the STANDARD pool service.  If you need smaller values, please use our TECH pool service.


&lt;/p&gt;Your Eurocircuits Team</description>
